# Qure Design System

Use this design system when building or refactoring UI. All tokens and variants are derived from Figma. Do not invent values.

**Entrypoint for routing:** `design-system-context-routing.mdc` (always apply).

All component rules (`ds-*.mdc`) have been rebuilt from Figma with Variables, Structure, Variants, States, and Implementation guidelines. Each rule references its Figma node.

