## Design System Setup

- **globals.css:** Define CSS variables for light/dark per `[data-theme]`; use only Figma variable values from design-system-tokens.
- **Tailwind config:** Extend theme with token references; no hardcoded values.
- **ThemeProvider:** Set `data-theme` on `<html>`; persist to localStorage; optionally respect `prefers-color-scheme`.
- **New project checklist:** Copy `.cursor/rules/`, create globals.css with token definitions from design-system-tokens.mdc, add Tailwind config extending tokens, add ThemeProvider.
